## Color Palette

### Primary Colors

```css
/* Primary Dark - Headers, primary text, navigation */
--color-primary-dark: #0d192c;

/* Secondary Dark - Secondary text, borders, subtle elements */
--color-secondary-dark: #0a393d;

/* Accent 1 - CTAs, success states, active elements */
--color-accent-1: #14b8a1;

/* Accent 2 - Alerts, errors, urgent actions */
--color-accent-2: #e6262a;

/* Background - Main background, cards, clean surfaces */
--color-background: #fcfcfb;
```

### Color Usage Rules

- **Primary Dark** (`#0D192C`): Use for headers, primary text, navigation elements
- **Secondary Dark** (`#0A393D`): Use for secondary text, borders, subtle UI elements
- **Accent 1** (`#14B8A1`): Use for CTAs, success states, active/hover states
- **Accent 2** (`#E6262A`): Use for alerts, errors, urgent actions, Swiss identity
- **Background** (`#FCFCFB`): Use for main backgrounds, cards, clean surfaces

### Accessibility Requirements

- Ensure WCAG 2.1 AA contrast ratios
- Test with colorblind users
- Provide alternative indicators beyond color
- Use sufficient contrast for all text

